            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-style:normal;">Click</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered"> the sketch-element in </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Mechanism A</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered"> you want to &apos;copy&apos; as Reference-Geometry to </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Mechanism B.</text></li>
